title: + MEI Weihui of College of Education Speaks at 4th UNESCO-APEID Meeting on Entrepreneurship Education ...
text: ( Source : Zhejiang University ) Oct. 20, 2015 MEI Weihui , an associate professor of the College of Education , Zhejiang University, was invited to attend the 4th UNESCO-APEID Meeting on Entrepreneurship Education in Thailand on October 12-14.
